STATE EX REL. NAVISTAR, INC.
v.
INDUS. COMM. 2018-1416 Supreme Court of Ohio. February 11, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MEDIATION MATTERS

The following case has been returned to the regular docket under S.Ct.Prac.R. 19.01. Appellant shall file a brief within 40 days, and the parties shall otherwise proceed in accordance with S.Ct.Prac.R. 16.02 through 16.07. As provided in S.Ct.Prac.R. 16.07, the court may dismiss this case or take other action if the parties fail to timely file merit briefs.
